<div id="page-wrapper">
    <h1 class="page-header">Trap</h1>
    <div class="col-lg-4">
        <div class="panel panel-default">
            <div class="panel-heading">
                Steps to be followed to Trap a Request.
            </div>
            <div class="panel-body">
                <p class="lead"></p>
                <p>1) Click on any of the Secret URLs to trap a request.</p>
